text: Nestled on a sprawling 19k+ sq. ft. lot in an established neighborhood, this property offers a park-like setting in a vibrant rural community. With 4 bdrms, 2 bthrms, and 2 family rooms spread over 2 levels, providing comfortable living. Enjoy the updated kitchen, and step outside to a large back deck ideal for afternoon relaxation and entertaining. The huge fenced-in backyard, complete with trees and a rope swing, is a paradise for outdoor activities. W/a choice of Ferndale or Meridian schools both offering convenient bus pickups, your educational needs are well-catered for. This home is brimming with potential, allowing you to make it yours while enjoying the foundation it has been built upon. Recent updates include a presidential roof.

Looking for a nice private RV/camping recreational get away? If a tribal member verify with the tribe regarding water, sewer and electricity to the property to possibly build a home or put a manufactured home on the property - buyer to verify all possibilities...

Tucked away near the end of a quiet cul-de-sac, this newly remodeled home offers a cozy, well laid out floor plan. The main level hosts a living room with lots of natural light, dining room and kitchen complete with quartz countertops and SS appliances, a spacious primary bedroom with a dual access bathroom & a walk in closet, along with a laundry room that includes a washer/dryer. On the second level there is an additional bathroom along with two bedrooms. Step out onto the back deck to see the spacious, fully fenced backyard. Located close to the Lakeway shopping center, parks and trails. You won't want to miss this one!

For those seeking a blend of peaceful living and convenient access to outdoor adventures, this 2-bedroom house in Maple Falls is an ideal choice. Its park-like setting, combined with the comfort and functionality of the home, offers a unique living experience that is hard to find elsewhere. One of the standout features of this property is its expansive outdoor space. The backyard is a true haven, which includes a big outdoor shop, greenhouse, dog run, tree house, landscaping, and fruit trees. Recent upgrades include a new roof, siding, and heat pump. The house is located at the end of a quiet cul-de-sac. This unique property has so much to offer! Schedule you're showing today!

This amazing home is uniquely positioned for wonderful privacy yet is minutes from 241 acres of Whatcom Falls Park beauty & miles of Galbraith Mountain biking trails. Enjoy custom architectural design, expansive views of mature trees, multiple outdoor spaces & the flat, sunny front yard perfect for gardening & relaxing during long summer evenings. Wooden ceilings & built-ins bring a wonderful timeless warmth to the home & cooks will love the spacious kitchen w/ abundant storage & work space. The 4th bedroom is currently used as media/office space. Storage options are endless in the massive 2 car garage w/ an extra tall ceiling. Located on a quiet cul-de-sac yet less than 10 minutes to multiple shopping options & I-5 access. A must see home!

VERY NICE MID CENTURY UPDATED RAMBLER. BRICK AND HARDY PLANK SIDING, new roof and gutters in the last 2 years. Hardwood floors throughout with tile in the kitchen. Kitchen is really nice stainless steel and solid surface countertops! Bathroom has been updated nicely . Washer & Dryer are also included in sale. Fireplace for those special evenings. Large fenced backyard with three apple trees, cement patio, dog run, and very nice storage shed. Behind carport is a fully finished store room. The home comes with completed plans for ensuite primary bathroom and a garage. This location and a .26 Acre lot near the high school is worth your time to view!

Prepare to be blown away by this stunning Bellingham dream home! Enter your custom front door & youll be greeted with high-end, luxury finishes throughout. Beautiful wood floors bring you up to your fabulous open concept living rm & kitchen, complete with quartzite counters, eating bar & pantry. Enjoy your spacious primary bedroom with slider to your covered top deck, walk-in closet & luxury en-suite bath...relax in the oversized glass shower with two shower heads! Plenty of room for hobbies w/multi-level outdoor spaces surrounded by fresh, easy maintenance landscaping, and 2 car garage w/plenty of storage that currently doubles as a gym. Located in Gate 1 of Sudden Valley, youll have access to the best in lakeside living & amenities.

Discover 640 Northview St. in Cordata, where contemporary solar living is complemented by stunning mountain and golf course views. This home, better than new, offers an open concept layout that artfully merges elegance and practicality. The modern kitchen is adorned with premium finishes, a generous island, and a walk-in pantry with extra flex space. A mini-split heat pump guarantees comfort in all seasons, while solar panels boost energy savings. Prepped for electric vehicle charging. The fully fenced yard provides a peaceful retreat with amazing sunrise and sunset views. Benefit from nearby attractions like the brand-new Cordata Park, scenic bike lanes, trails, and shopping.

Rare, well cared for 2, 065 SF, 3 bed 2.5 bath townhome w/tons of natural light. New 40k kitchen remodel with custom cabinets, quartz countertops & SS appliances. Primary bedroom ensuite with double vanity & walk-in closet. Large front porch and back deck in a peaceful, quiet, treed setting. Outdoor firepit area w/space for entertaining. Large shed for storage. Spacious garage w/workbench & extra storage. Recently remodeled laundry room and 4+ parking spaces. Highly desirable neighborhood near the heart of Fairhaven's historic district and its charming pubs, restaurants, bookstores and gift shops. 5 minute walk to the Ferry Terminal, Amtrak Station, Community Boating Center, and Marine Park. Steps away from the Interurban Trail too!

Fully-Remodeled home packed w/ stunning designer updates! Open main floorplan w/ soaring vaulted ceilings, gorgeous wood beams & trim, modern laminate floors, living room w/ incredible floor-to-ceiling fireplace, sunny dining room, 2 beds/1 full bath. Chef's kitchen w/ dazzling tile backsplash, breakfast bar, pantry, & SS appliances. Upstairs loft-style flex area, plus the luxurious primary suite w/ walk-in closet & custom designer tile shower w/ dual heads & built-in shelves/bench...Truly a must-see! Downstairs boasts the 4th bedroom, modern half bath, utility room, & huge Rec Room w/ wet bar & ample room for hobbies & relaxation. Low maintenance backyard w/ large partially-covered deck & serene greenbelt views. Brand New Roof in May 2024!

Rustic fixer historic farmhouse on just under an acre lot in rural Birch Bay neighborhood. Major FIXER being sold AS IS and a possible great sweat equity producer for the right buyer. All utilities are in and home needs comprehensive exterior & interior renovations to make habitable once again.

5 beautiful acres in sought after area. Picturesque land with potential view of Mt Baker. Water share available through Deer Creek Water Association and power in the street. Wetlands survey complete. Choose your building site. Prime area. in Meridian School district just down the street from Shuksan Golf Course. Don't miss your chance to own it today!

Comfortable and clean move in ready three-bedroom, two bath, 1296 SQ. FT. home with large kitchen and casual dining space. Master with ensuite, two addition bedrooms and full bath. Freshly painted inside and out, forced air heat, back deck with built in bench seating and lots of room to park your RV. Located in a low traffic private setting with back yard abutting an acreage parcel, just a short walk to Lily Point Marine Park. Great get away home or full-time residence that you can enjoy the year round. Furnishings are available.

Welcome to this stunning modern contemporary home in Ferndale, WA! This 4-bedroom gem is loaded with custom upgrades and features. The kitchen boasts a wine refrigerator, a pop-up phone charger, under-cabinet lighting, and upgraded appliances. The living room is a light-filled haven with large windows, a gas fireplace, and a sparkling chandelier. Enjoy amazing outdoor entertaining with an extended covered patio, complete with lighting, a fan, and a fire pit area. The beautifully landscaped backyard also offers privacy trees and a new lawn. With added touches like stair lighting and upgraded bathrooms, this home combines luxury and functionality. Don't miss the office's upper deck with breathtaking views of Mount Baker and the Twin Sisters!

Nestled amidst the serene beauty of rolling hills & pastures, this 5-acre property offers breathtaking views & 2 tranquil ponds. Main floor w/ spacious primary suite + updated spa-like bath & an open layout boasting a living room w/huge windows, gas fireplace, & vaulted ceilings. Designer kitchen w/ modern cabinets, counters, tile backsplash, SS appliances & island. Head down to an expansive recreation room, office, 2 more bedrooms, & a full guest bath. Outside is your own slice of paradise: wraparound deck, fenced pastures, fruit & nut trees, multiple outbuildings. New roof, garage doors, water heater, & whole-house water filter. Updated Trex front/back porches, upgraded barn, greenhouse, & shed. The ultimate blend of luxury & tranquility!

The Ivy by MainVue Homes at Horizon is a stunning design you do not want to miss. Upon entry find a soaring Two-Story Foyer a corner set a Home Office. Deeper into the home, the Two-Story Great Room is paired perfectly with a sophisticated Dining room and mutually connected Gourmet Kitchen flush with 3cm Quartz counters, Stainless Steel Appliances, and a Grand Butlers Pantry. For even more space, a main floor Multi-Purpose Room is tucked just off the kitchen. Upstairs, look out onto the Great Room from the front-facing Leisure room that leads to three secondary bedrooms and the luxurious Grand Suite. Customer registration policy: Buyers Broker to visit or be registered on Buyers 1st visit for full Commission is reduced.

Very well-built, well-maintained, single level mid-century home in the Columbia neighborhood. House features 2 bedrooms, 2 baths, almost 1300 sq ft, on a large level lot w/ alley access. Interior has an open floor plan: the main living areas feature arched doorways and the living room has coved ceilings & inviting sight lines. The cheery classic kitchen has the original Youngstown cabinetry. Home is heated with a natural gas hydronic system and a gas fireplace for ambiance. Other features include a walk-in pantry, outdoor deck, patio, sheds & fenced yard. The garage space has been updated and creates a flexible living space. The home is close to schools, shopping, brew pubs, parks, trails, the waterfront and easy access to I-5.

This beautifully updated rustic rambler boasts a newer roof, flooring, appliances, hot water tank. and much more! With 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this property offers ample space for comfortable living. The large great room features a cozy gas fireplace, perfect for gatherings and relaxation. The primary room has a large walk in closet and ensuit! Situated on a private, flat lot, this well-maintained home is ready for you to move in and enjoy. Interior trim, barn doors, saloon doors are all local reclaimed wood. Park and trails very close!

Natural light abounds in this incredibly spacious, 2 bed, 2 full bath condo unit. Quiet, tranquil, and clean. Bask in the afternoon sun and catch sunset colors from your top-floor, west-facing private balcony. This gently lived-in unit not only has an abundance of storage, it also has a closet large enough for an in-home office. The open-concept dining/living space makes it perfect for hosting. Includes in-unit stacked washer/dryer. Minutes to Costco, WCC, and all that Cordata has to offer, you'll love living so close to shopping, health care, walking and biking trails, and more. Both bedrooms have attached bathrooms with giant walk-in closets, powder areas, and tubs with showers. Don't forget to check out the clubhouse, too. Must see!

Introducing your newly renovated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom Sumas home! This 1446-square-foot gem has received a complete makeover, inside and out. Fresh paint graces the exterior, complemented by new gutters. Inside, every inch has been transformed, from wall to wall and floor to ceiling. Revel in the brand-new vinyl flooring, a modern kitchen with all-new appliances, and updated bathrooms boasting contemporary fixtures. Relax in the inviting sunroom with your morning cup of coffee, or unwind on the back covered porch, perfect for enjoying the beautiful weather. Plus, with the stunning mountains of Sumas just minutes away, this home is an outdoor enthusiast's dream. Experience the joy of a fully renovated home combined with the allure of nature

Step into a piece of Bellingham's past, where history and modern convenience converge in this meticulously restored 4-bedroom historic home. This home features timeless charm with its original hardwood floors and intricate moldings but also boasts updated finishes. Freshly painted interior, new light fixtures, and brand new stainless appliances make this home move in ready. The spacious layout includes a formal dining room and a cozy den, perfect for both intimate gatherings and larger celebrations. Outside, the gardens, mature fruit trees, and newly refinished deck provide an inviting space. Detached garage with period windows and 220 is ready for workshop or studio. Come enjoy the A/C in this bright cool character filled home.

Nestled in the heart of North Bellingham this spacious 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo offers spacious living across 1493 square feet. Enhanced with upgraded appliances in kitchen and laundry. Large covered deck off of the living room. Extra large primary bedroom boasts a walk-in closet for ample storage and en-suite bathroom with jetted tub and shower. Water, sewer and garbage included in the HOA dues plus two assigned parking spaces, including one under the carport! This condo presents a perfect blend of comfort and convenience, promising a delightful lifestyle in a coveted location just minutes from the mall, grocery stores, I5, hospitals, restaurants and all Bellingham has to offer.

OCEAN VIEW! Custom built West facing home in Semiahmoo Resort with over 4, 700 square feet with commanding sea and skyscape views from nearly every room with world class sunsets! Stunning yet comfortable, spacious yet cozy, bright & light throughout with walls of windows and easy main floor living, including the primary suite. Multiple living areas for everyone... a great room, dining, family, recreation room, plus a secondary primary suite.. An expansive sundeck and large covered patio are nestled amongst the mature landscaping and manicured level yard. Ideally located in the desirable and exclusive Boundary Ridge neighborhood with a gated entry. Enjoy Semiahmoo's attractions - clubhouse, restaurant, marina and an award winning golf course!

Development Opportunity! Solid, established Lynden home in expanding commercial area of town. 3 bedrooms, 2 full bath, 3 living areas including partially finished basement with outside access. 34, 848 sqft. lot is Zoned for RM-2 could support two 4-plex units plus 3-plex if existing residence is removed or convert/remodel current residence to duplex. City Sewer Line recently install on the South property line with free connection available for current residence.

A modern vibe on a tranquil .67-acre lot in Bellingham. Every room in this home captures the surrounding lush green views. The gourmet chef's kitchen boasts a 48 cooktop, quartz counters & custom-tailored cabinets that flow seamlessly into the backyard entertainment oasis. The owners suite features Elfa shelving, designer bamboo window coverings, and a spa-like en-suite bthrm with a soaking tub. Guest bdrms have built-in desks. Entertainment is effortless w/ a wet bar, great ADU potential w/its own entrance. 2 gas-insert fireplaces add warmth and ambiance to the 2 lg living areas. This home is tech-savvy w/Ethernet, Nest thermostats & an EV plug. Located in the City, on a dead-end street offering privacy with easy Interurban trail access.

A rare Rosewood Lane condominium tucked away next to the Interurban Trail and Fairhaven Park. A stone's throw away from Fairhaven Village and all it has to offer. This beautifully cared for and updated 3 bdrm home is the perfect blend of easy living and high style. The gorgeous kitchen is bathed in natural light from the generous skylights in the cathedral ceiling. The living area and deck look out over mature trees and the Padden Creek nature area beyond. The home has been skillfully and stylishly updated. Fireplaces on both levels, new fixtures and furnace. Two bedrooms and full-bath on upper level and primary suite with 3/4 bath on main. Well run HOA. Attached, private garage w/30 AMP dryer outlet gives the option to charge a car.

Welcome to your dream retreat near Locust Beach! This meticulously remodeled, mid-century rambler offers the epitome of luxury living. Spanning 1, 045 sq ft on a vast 11, 730 sq ft lot, this home boasts breathtaking views of Mt. Baker. Every detail has been thoughtfully considered, from the sleek stainless-steel appliances to the elegant granite countertops. The entire home has been renovated, top to bottom, including roof, all new windows, trim, kitchen, fixtures and bathroom. With 2 beds and 1 bath, this residence is perfect for those seeking a serene escape just blocks from the beach a short bike ride to DT Bellingham. Don't miss the chance to make this exquisite property your own!

Opportunity waits for builders and remodelers in the coveted Cornwall Park neighborhood! This property, situated in a prime location, presents a rare chance for development or renovation, with the potential for a rehab loan to unlock its full potential. While the existing home is a complete fixer-upper, the true value lies in the 4792 square feet level lot, boasting alley access and already equipped with utilities. Conveniently near Haggen Foods, Cornwall Park, schools, hospitals, medical facilities, and transit options, this location is ideal for both residents and investors alike. The forthcoming implementation of House Bill 1110, legalizing middle housing in residential neighborhoods, the future possibilities are even more enticing.

Fabulous home nestled in sought-after Lakeridge Estates! Recently remodeled kitchen boasts a new island, walk-in pantry, SS appliances, & sleek Quartz countertops. Main floor Primary Suite features a spacious walk-in closet, private bath with tub, shower, & double basins. Upstairs, discover 3 more bedrooms, including one with an added hobby alcove and extra closet space. Updates include a new fireplace surround with live edge mantle, refreshed laundry room, and upgraded upstairs bath. Enjoy enhanced comfort with a new furnace and A/C, plus all-new flooring and exterior paint. This home, built by Dave Turner, sits on a generous lot with fruit trees, a patio, and parking for small RV. Stroll to the nearby community pond and walking trails.

Affordable rambler on dead-end street in coveted westside of Lynden, close to amenities on extra-large town lot! Surrounded by beautiful mature landscaping, tucked back off the road, this one-story home boasts over 1, 500 sq ft, 3 bd, 1.5 bath w/attached garage. Huge sunny living room just off entry, extra den/office is great flex room, cozy brick gas fireplace in dining room open to kitchen. 3 great sized bedrooms & full bath down hall away from main living areas. Tons of storage in kitchen & extra storage room off garage. Sliding glass door off dining leads to a ginormous private backyard, perfect for play, entertaining, relaxing & more. Priced to move!

Experience coastal luxury with breathtaking views of the islands & bay! Vaulted ceilings & skylights fill this home with abundant natural light. Six fireplaces add warmth & elegance. Recently updated & beautifully appointed, this serene retreat has direct access to the Interurban Trail & five private beaches, & just four minutes from Fairhaven. The open floorplan effortlessly connects indoor & outdoor spaces, perfect for entertaining or relaxing. Upstairs, find a spacious executive office & a luxurious primary suite. Downstairs, there's a versatile suite/ADU with a 2nd kitchen & patio offering stunning views. This home also features a wine cellar, exercise space, sauna, & steam roomeverything you need for ultimate comfort and relaxation.

If you are looking for a place that will give you privacy and a peaceful setting then this is it. This home is situated on a shy level acre. The home has an easy living floor plan with living room, family room and spacious eating area. There is room to add a shop or fence an area for an animal or two, just use your imagination. There is a lot of potential for this property at a great price.

Expansive bay views in inspired custom home w/ AC heat pump & gas furnace. The floor to ceiling windows & vaulted hip-roofs give the home its sense of elegance & space w/ the wrap-around deck expanding the living outside. Each room is bathed in natural light while the trees provide privacy & serenity. Great Room & kitchen enjoy oak floors w/ vistas in most every location. The main flr primary suite takes full advantage of the view while offering walk-in closet, double vanity, & tiled shower with 3/8 frameless glass surround. Laundry is on the MAIN FLOOR, allowing NO-STEP LIVING. Two more bdrms & a den are in bsmnt w/ views. Don't miss the heated shop space (400 SF -not incl) & water feature. Enjoy the NEW ROOF & New Car Deck Driveway.

Beautiful custom home w/ outstanding panoramic views of the ocean, mountains, and city. This meticulously maintained four-season home offers 2 beds and 2 baths that is located close to the beach. Featuring an elevated open main living area with vaulted ceilings, and large windows for beautiful light. High-end details throughout including hardwood flooring, stainless steel appliances, custom millwork, steam shower, soaker tub, 9 ceilings on the main, composite decking, and an outdoor shower. Expansive wrap-around balcony to take in the ever-changing vistas and a covered deck perfect for a rainy day or entertaining. Beautiful gardens and mature planting that offer a private setting. Don't miss out on this Point Robert's gem!

Imagine home becoming your haven of rest and ease. That doesn't have to be a dream anymore! Features like a no-step entry and easy one-level living are just the beginning! Enjoy all-season comfort with a mini-split and cozy gas fireplace. Easy-breezy kitchen cleanup meets luxurious design with quartz countertops, an undermount sink, and a waterfall island. Retreat to your primary bedroom with enveloping cove lighting. In the ensuite, the refinement continues with double showerheads and vanities, a bidet, a large walk-in closet, and heated tile floors. Enjoy gardening but want a no-maintenance lawn? The private backyard, with turf grass, terraces, fruit trees, and more was designed with you in mind! Here's your invitation- come fall in love!

Beautifully updated 3-bed, 2.5-bathroom residence with a versatile den upstairs that can effortlessly serve as a 4th bedroom. Brand New Furnace/AC, updates throughout & remodeled bathrooms, adding a touch of contemporary elegance. Residents enjoy access to a playground & community garden. The home's prime location offers close proximity to the newly developed 25-acre Cordata Park, featuring expansive green spaces, various activity areas, & picturesque pathways ideal for leisurely strolls or active pursuits. Small HOA fee covers front yard maintenance, ensuring a pristine exterior without the hassle. Don't miss this opportunity to own a meticulously cared-for home in a vibrant community that combines comfort, convenience, and modern living.

Welcome to The Ridge in Blaine, WA! This beautiful single-family home features 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, offering comfortable, single-level living with no steps. The large, open main floor living area is perfect for modern lifestyles, and the covered back living area allows you to enjoy the outdoors year-round. High-end finishes include luxury vinyl flooring, quartz countertops, and a slab on grade foundation for low-maintenance living. This home backs up to a greenbelt, providing privacy and a serene natural backdrop. Conveniently located near downtown Blaine and I-5 for easy access to amenities. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity! $5, 000 Buyer Credit available with our preferred lender, Becky Farrar at Evergreen Home Loans.

Welcome to your dream getaway! Absolutely gorgeous furnished 2-bedroom, 1 bathroom move-in ready cottage. Everything has been tastefully updated including the kitchen, full bathroom with tub and shower, flooring, electrical and septic system. Fabulous open layout and tons of natural light make it feel very spacious and comfortable yet cozy at the same time. Other features include a wood burning fireplace, bamboo floors and a large veranda at the front plus a new 400 sq. ft. deck at the back to while away the hours or entertain friends. Large shed for all your storage needs. Walking distance to the beach, Saltwater Caf, Kiniski's Reef Tavern, library, community center, grocery store and post office. Golf course and Lighthouse Park are close by also. If you are looking for that perfect place to write that book, take up painting or to be simply "one with nature" and enjoy some peace and tranquility away from the hustle and bustle of the city, this is the place you want to be. Be sure to check out the online Video Tour.

Beautiful 2-Story Craftsman Well Appointed Upon a Large Double Lot at the End of the Cul de Sac! Located Near Reed Lake This 3 Bed 2.5 Bath 1889 SqFt Home Offers Privacy and Mountain Views! Living Room with Cozy Gas FP Opens to Dining Area & Spacious Kitchen with Center Island, Granite Counters & Pantry. Separate Den Could Also Be Used as Office. Powder Room and Newly Refinished Laundry Room Complete the Main Level. Upper-Level Features New Luxury Vinyl Flooring, Two Guest Bedrooms & Full Guest Bath. Primary Suite with WIC and 5-Piece Attached Bath. Property Also Includes Fully Fenced Backyard, New 18x36 Pergola Over Concrete Patio, Mature Landscaping & RV Parking. Glenhaven Lakes Club Amenities Include Seasonal Pool, Clubhouse & Two Lakes.

Fantastic home in a great neighborhood close to BTC and bellingham trail system. 3 bedroom, 1 bath house on huge lot that is potentially subdividable (buyer to verify). Freshly painted inside and out. New vinyl flooring, washer, dryer and stove/oven. Newer roof in the last 10 years and solar panels that are direct connected to keep power bills low. Recent tree work done so house is light and bright and the John Deer mower conveys.

This captivating custom home on a coveted 7.72 acre gardener's paradise will take your breath away. 17ft vaulted ceilings allow sunshine to sprawl through this open floor plan with abundant windows & gorgeous hardwood flooring. Charming French doors frame a stylish main level office, & central stairs lead to a sunlit loft with guest room potential. Timeless cherry cabinetry in both kitchen & bathrooms. Massive glass doors present your sweeping 40ft porch inspiring unending outdoor solace or entertainment. Spacious detached 24 x 40 shop with large sliding door for all hobbies with electric & 50amp. Enjoy lush landscaping, plus a private sanctuary of PNW trails w/ ancient fir trees and an acre wide meadow ready for your imagination.

Meticulously clean & maintained 1 story condo w/detached true 2 car garage & beautiful views of treed creek below. Excellent location across the street from urgent care, dental, doctor's office - minutes from Fairway Center amenities & downtown Lynden. Great open floor plan w/tons of windows to let natural light into living room, dining & kitchen. Cozy gas fireplace for winter months. Spacious eat-in kitchen w/stainless steel appliances, granite counters, & large peninsula bar. Owner's suite has full ensuite bath w/tons of storage + walk in closet. Beautiful hardwood floors t/out entry/hall kitchen/dining. Enjoy peaceful views of mother nature year-round, while only being minutes from shopping, health care, & more!

Looking for a spacious 4 bdrm/2.5 bath home designed over 3, 000 sq ft, & happens to have gorgeous Mt Baker views? You've found it! Along w/a traditional living, family, & dining rooms, this home also features a finished basement (completed in '19) w/bonus room, bdrm, multipurpose room, & plumbed for a bathroom...all accented by exposed beam work & new flooring. Enjoy modern upgrades including new siding, new decking, & heat pump for year-round comfort. Even the deck doors open outward to maximize the flow. The expansive lot not only offers stunning mountain views but also includes a sport court for outdoor activities or use as space for that boat/RV. This property combines modern amenities w/scenic beauty, making it a perfect retreat.

Experience epic fun at Grand Bay condos beach! Vibrant seaside-style resort life w/in golf cart zone life with Birch Bay restaurants, Beach Cat Brewery, library, parks. Full time or second home. 2nd floor condo w/elevator outside entry w/south-facing balcony & partial water view. Fully turnkey. Stylish finishes, radiant floor heat in baths. 1, 023 SF, 2 BR, 2 full BA. Built 2010. On site amenities- community hot tub, storage for kayaks, paddleboards & bikes. Association owns grass field by mouth of Terrell Creek & beach rights, firepits in front. 2 pets OK. Dues inc. maintenance, insurance, garbage. Beach berm in front w/ 1.5 mile of level surface. Small boats can anchor in front Aug-Oct crabbing season. Week minimum rentals OK. Sunsets!

Discover this immaculate south Bellingham home within a few blocks to Lake Padden Park with miles of Trails, Golf and minutes to historic Fairhaven. This move-in-ready home offers high-quality craftsmanship throughout. Enjoy the park-like setting with absolute privacy and partial Bay views. Entertaining kitchen with nook and bar seating, opens to the family room with a gas fireplace. Formal dining and main floor den or living room. Primary with luxury ensuite and walk-in closet. Finished basement with a full bath plus fireplace, ideal for a mother-in-law suite. Exceptional outdoor living with a walk-around porch, gazebo, huge backyard deck and fire pit area. Ample parking. Detached garage with workshop area. A magical Southside wonderland!

Classic, timeless and traditional single story rambler offers an incredible 2, 500 sqft of living space. It's amazing how perfect the room size is in this home from the warm and inviting great room to the formal dining room. The private & sunny wrap around deck makes for a back yard of low maintenance living. Great exposure offers lots of natural light. Spacious kitchen is ideal for entertaining with easy access off the formal dining & breakfast nook. Excellent counter space & wonderful storage through out. The two car garage is extra deep. Two private guest suites, separate art studio with private entrance off the primary suite. Comfortable primary bedroom with sitting space, walk-in shower & custom closets. Exceptional value--a must see.

This luxury home centrally located in Bellingham is ready for it's new owners! Walk into your open concept living room, dining, room and kitchen with a walk-in pantry. The oversized patio boasts sun throughout the day and is adjacent to protected land for extra privacy! Your two car garage has an extra storage nook with plenty of room for your bikes or a small workshop. Walk up the stairs (don't miss the peek-a-boo Mt Baker view!) to your primary bedroom. This oversized primary has an en suite bathroom and his and hers walk-in closets. Down the hall you will find an additional full bathroom, laundry room and two additional bedrooms. Don't miss out on this stunning home close to I-5, Cordata Park, Dining, Shopping & More!

Welcome to your South Hill water view condo, completely remodeled in 2019 and meticulously cared for. This end unit has gorgeous views of Bellingham Bay and many bells and whistles. Everything like new, + zero stairs! Attached 2-car carport takes you directly to your private outdoor entrance via land bridge. High-end LG appliances, Hertco cabinets, quartz counters, gas fireplace, custom tiled showers w/ frameless glass, quality LVP flooring, & plush carpet in bedrooms. Brand new recessed ceiling heat pump for year 'round heating and cooling. Master has huge ensuite w/ his & her sinks, large rainhead shower, & walk-in closet. 2nd bed also w/ walk-in closet. LG W/D & sink in utility room. Built-ins in every closet. Hurry, this won't last.

Beautiful one-level Cordata home with fantastic designer upgrades. Custom chefs kitchen with tall white shaker cabinets, Bosch S/S appliances, marble and glass backsplash, and a full-drawer spacious island that makes entertaining a dream. Stunning floor-to-ceiling stone fireplace, 9 ceilings, quartz countertops, under-mount sinks, and engineered wood flooring throughout bring this home to a whole new level of luxury living. Custom upgrades include an ironwood, wrought iron rail front porch, A/C, Maxx tub, fully tiled baths, designer lighting, a 52 backyard deck, and Xeriscape landscaping for effortless yard maintenance. Nothing here is builder-grade! If you've been looking for the one you have found it!

Top-floor corner unit in the heart of Lynden! Stunning views of Mount Baker and farmlands from the spacious private deck. One of the two bedrooms features a Murphy bed and built-in shelving and drawers. Solid wood cabinets and brand new vinyl flooring in kitchen/dining and bathroom. The Solatube skylight provides ambient natural daylight in the kitchen. In-unit washer & dryer is included (washer is brand new). Brand new water heater. Comparatively low HOA dues cover water/sewer/garbage. One assigned parking space plus ample guest parking. No rental cap.

2, 250 square foot industrial/storage condominium conveniently located in the Irongate Industrial Business Park. Quality built with steel construction and metal roofs for longevity and low maintenance in mind, and a gated community, STOREHOUSE, that is secure and accessible 24/7. Features include 2 ADA bathrooms, 2 large 14x16 overhead doors with windows and automated openers, high vaulted ceilings, wired for 220 and additional outlets, lighting, shelving, epoxy floors, and so much more. Why rent when you can own.

Charming 1896 gem nestled in the South Hill, Happy Valley, and Fairhaven convergence zone offers affordability, convenience, & walkability. This is your jump-off point to downtown Fairhaven, WWU, Interurban Trail, Chuckanut Mountains, Taylor Dock, and more! Fresh interior paint and new carpet! Solar panels keep energy bills low and the gas fireplace keeps you cozy and warm. Swing open the french doors & bask in the sun on your 525 sqft deck with a hot tub! The updated kitchen and electrical are sure to please and the enclosed sunroom offers options for storage, a greenhouse, and more. One bedroom and full bath on the main & two beds plus walk-in attic storage upstairs. South side roof replaced 2023, solar 2018, kitchen 2017 & more!

LARGE SINGLE FAMILY LOT - Located in the new East Maple Ridge development. Corner lot with 6, 891 square feet. All services available with the water General Facility Fees paid ($3k+ savings). The development includes community parks, sidewalks and lots of waking trails, picnic tables and a planned dog park. Above the Ridge of H Street with a close commute to town, schools, I5 access and the US/Canada Border.

Dreaming of building your dream home in Birch Bay? Look no further then this ideal vacant lot! This pristine location is surrounded by lush greenery and stunning natural beauty. Providing ample space for custom home designs, gardens, and outdoor living areas. Enjoy the tranquility of rural living while being just minutes away from downtown Blaine, top-rated schools, scenic parks, and convenient access to I-5 and the Canadian border. Septic design was previously applied for and approved, but has since expired. Water is available with Birch Bay Water and Sewer in the street. Dont miss this unique opportunity to build your ideal retreat in a prime location!

Discover a rare opportunity nestled just off Barkley Boulevard, boasting stunning views of the Bay and City of Bellingham. This spacious residence spans over 1800 square feet, featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths upstairs, a 3/4 bath downstairs, and generous dining space leading to a fully fenced backyard. The third bedroom upstairs is versatile, easily transformable into an office space, featuring a sliding door granting access to the deck, providing unparalleled views of the Bay. Enjoy direct access to neighborhood trails and the convenience of Barkley Village shopping center just minutes away.

Superior custom built home. 3 bedroom 2 bath on a large quiet lot. Many built in alcoves and custom features throughout. Brilliant living room with coffered ceilings and oversized windows allowing views to the private backyard. Bright kitchen with garden window and spacious breakfast nook. Extremely roomy master suite with walk through closet, jetted tub and separate jetted tub. You'll be pleasantly comfortable walking on the radiant floor heating system with multiple zones. Recently painted inside and out, new tile flooring , appliances and more! Oversized 576 s.f. 2 car garage and attic trussed for extra storage. Don't miss the bay and mountain views from the outside roof height deck.

Expansive city, bay & mountain view from this better than new King Mountain stunner! Radiating PNW charm, the sun drenched interior delights with light & bright on-trend finishes and the open concept design sought after by the modern buyer. The main level primary suite is privately tucked away from the other bedrooms & features vaulted ceilings, a luxurious en-suite bath & spacious walk in closet. Convenient office/den is ideally located on the main level and you'll love watching the sunsets from your deck or quickly accessing the neighborhood park. Additional bedrooms and bonus space on lower level + unfinished area with potential to be a 4th bedroom or...you decide! Loads of storage throughout + fully fenced yard.

Welcome to your new home. Meticulously maintained home. Fantastic bonus room upstairs near the bedrooms. Outside you have a great yard, relaxing deck for entertaining in the summer and don't miss the husky hut for the fall football games. Great central location and Bellingham schools. Close to Lake Whatcom and Galbraith Mtn trail system.

Mt. Baker view property. Large centrally located site with development potential. Currently in open space so build your home on this large property and pay low annual taxes. Irrigation rights for livestock or agriculture. Minutes to Ferndale or Bellingham. Easy I-5 access.

Come home to luxury living on gorgeous Lake Samish with ~90 feet of lake frontage! Custom-built in 2012 and thoughtfully designed to maximize ease of life on the lake! Every detail is thoughtfully considered, from private balconies off of bedrooms & office, to the expansive main deck that includes entertaining & grilling space, to the private dock & low-maintenance landscaping. Air conditioning and fire suppression system throughout, and hot water on demand. ADU over garage w/ exterior access, 1BD/1BA, kitchen + living, W/D in unit. Basement includes space with kitchen, 2 BD/1 BA + laundry; potential to add wall to create a separate apartment. Just 20 minutes to downtown, this beautiful home offers the best of south Bellingham living!

Opportunity to own a unit in one of downtowns most convenient locations! This building offers an interior courtyard, secure entry, a large secure parking garage and an elevator. This 2-bedroom one bath unit has an oversized sliding door in the living room which floods in tons of natural light. Just a couple blocks from the Saturday market and walking distance to the university makes this a versatile home for anyone. With no rental cap this could be considered for an investor's portfolio as well. Don't miss out on the chance to be in the heart of all that Bellingham has to offer!
neighborhoods: City Center Bellingham, Downtown District Bellingham

text: NEW PRICE! NEW PRICE! Nestled in the heart of Custer. The sprawling 29.11+/-acre farm has 3 wells - 310 ft in the pasture area, 24ft by the road side, 18ft closer to the main house. Property zoned R10- septic field for each 10 acres. Forestry plan in place. Timbered in 1991, trees replaced n 1992. This picturesque property boasts mature fruit trees: Yellow Delicious, Red Delicious, Jona Red, Jona Gold, Asian Pears, sweet pears, peach trees, plum trees & more. Large, sturdy 2000 SF workshop. The charming 1569 SF 3 BD, 1.5 BA home, with basement - In addition, there is a 1 BD, .75 BA mother-in-law suite attached to the carport. This farm is more than a property - It's a wonderful investment property. Great value for your money. Don't miss out.

Ready to take on a fixer? Built in 1961, this charming fixer-upper near Maple Beach once shone brightly, but time has taken its toll, and it now awaits a new owner ready to make it shine. A cozy wood-burning fireplace is at the heart of the home, while the kitchen features vintage appliances. There are two cozy bedrooms and a 3/4 bath. The lot will require power and water connections. Soils test show the lot is suitable for an on-site sewage system. Priced to move quickly; call the listing broker for more details.

1, 500 square foot (30x50) industrial/storage condominium conveniently located in the Irongate Industrial Business Park. Quality built with steel construction and metal roofs for longevity and low maintenance in mind, and a gated community, STOREHOUSE, that is secure and accessible 24/7. Features include an ADA bathroom, large 14x16 overhead door with windows and automated opener, high vaulted ceiling, wired for 220 and additional outlets, lighting, shelving, epoxy floors, and so much more. Why rent when you can own.
